== Confirm Email

**Authentication not required**

When a user signs up, the welcome email will contain a deep link with a fallback of `<front_url>/confirm-email/<id>/<token>`.

[source]
----
POST /users/:id/confirm-email
----

=== Input

[cols="2,1,5"]
|===
|Name |Type |Description

|`token` | `string` | Token from the URL in the email sent.
|===

=== Deep Link Data

[cols="2,1,5"]
|===
|Name |Type |Description

|`$desktop_url` | `string` | The web URL to perform confirm email.
|`type` | `string` | Always `confirm-email`
|`user` | `integer` | The ID of the user who is confirming their email.
|`token` | `string` | The verification token.
|===


